menu_item.name: Honey Vanilla Bean Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: A vanilla to end all vanillas. Made with Fair Trade vanilla beans that are warm and complex in flavor and a perfect partner for grass-grazed milk. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).

menu_item.name: Salted Peanut Butter with Chocolate Flecks Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: Salted and roasted ground peanuts with grass-grazed milk and crunchy, dark chocolate flecks. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).

menu_item.name: Salty Caramel Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: Fire-toasted sugar with sea salt, vanilla, and grass-grazed milk. A perfect balance of salty and sweet. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).

menu_item.name: Gooey Butter Cake Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: Cream cheese ice cream layered with crumbles of vanilla cake and a swirl of caramel-butterscotch sauce. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).

menu_item.name: Brambleberry Crisp Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: Oven-toasted oat streusel and a sweet-tart “brambleberry” jam of blackberries and blackcurrants layered throughout vanilla ice cream. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).

menu_item.name: Darkest Chocolate Ice Cream (3.6 oz)
menu_item.description: Mouth-filling and palate-gripping with a pleasingly dry finish. The most amount of Fair-Trade-Certified cocoa possible and the least amount of anything else. Single serve ice cream in ready-to-roam 3.6 oz. cup (with a spoon under the lid).
